data.name: richTextBox2.Text
data.value: For users who have ASUS notebooks after upgrading to Windows 8 / 8.1 stops functioning the screen brightness. Run program and use keys F5 to brightness down, and F6 to brightness up. Note: If You want this program start with Windows, add shortcut of SetBrightness.exe to C:\Users\$User_profile\AppData\ Roaming\Microsoft\Windows\Start Menu\Programs\Startup
